title: Is H.R.? 6666 Allowing the removal of COVID-19 patients from their homes?
subtitle: The viral sites claimed that the proposed legislation of the United States Republic of America, Bobby Rush, would replace constitutional rights during the outbreak of the Corona virus.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: COVID-19 to test access and communication with all (TRACE), or H.R. 6666, would authorize the CAVID-19 test groups run by the Federal Government to enter American homes and impose a test against the will of residents, and then "take" those who have a positive test to quarantine sites.
